sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User/UI
  participant W as Workflow UI Adapter
  participant H as DataCloudHttpServer
  participant P as PipelineCheckpointHandler
  participant S as Pipeline Services
  participant DB as Persistence
  U->>W: save pipeline/checkpoint
  W->>H: HTTP /api/v1/pipelines or /checkpoints
  H->>P: dispatch
  P->>S: translate workflow to pipeline model
  S->>DB: persist state
  DB-->>S: saved record
  S-->>P: response DTO
  P-->>H: HTTP payload
  H-->>W: success response
  W-->>U: updated workflow UI

